            <title><![CDATA[Arc Raiders "Isn't About Shooting Other Players," So Don't Expect More PvP Stuff]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/arc-raiders-isnt-about-shooting-other-players-so-dont-expect-more-pvp-stuff/1100-6537242/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
